{"tid":1824145,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年區議會成功向政府 爭取民生政策措施","createTime":"2020-01-14T08:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T12:20:31.000Z","uid":239516,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"badf9037971345e959b1c15c42f9bbf420a33222","tid":1824145,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=376717&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376717%26refer%3DShare&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerlmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=a15148b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376717%26refer%3DShare&h=ad9d2a24\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=376717&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n區議會成功爭取主要協助長者及基層人士重點措施如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 改革長者生活津貼，普通津貼及高額津貼合二為一，每月津貼劃一至3585元，資產限額將提高至50萬元<br />\n<br />\n2. 長者2元乘車優惠放寬至60歲或以上長者<br />\n<br />\n3. 政府代月入少於7100元以下人士供強積金<br />\n<br />\n4. 法定假期由12天增至17天，分階段逐步推行<br />\n<br />\n5. 改善政府外判員工待遇<br />\n<br />\n6. 為輪候公屋超過3年以上及符合資格申請住戶發放現金津貼，直至首次獲編派公屋為止；非公屋、非綜援人士，以及為輪候公屋3年以下人士，制定較為寬鬆職津計劃發放津貼<br />\n<br />\n7. 研究推行「劏房」租務管制，由運輸及房屋局成立工作小組研究可行方案<br />\n<br />\n8. 過渡性房屋目標增加至額外5000個單位<br />\n<br />\n9. 關愛基金為失業人士擬定一項新現金津貼，為合資格人士發放最多三個月津貼<br />\n<br />\n10. 關愛基金為就業工時低人士設計現金津貼，申請條件稍後公布"},{"pid":"c00935aad9aa3b8a66303c84fedd1712cf89912f","tid":1824145,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"一齊多謝區議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1026449336e70537ddc5c07def4b781aa7ccb70f","tid":1824145,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"區議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857a3fd48856140277c5c75cd280e2994db80c03","tid":1824145,"uid":135628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"咁快就做到野<br />\n咁之前咁多年啲區議員搞乜<br />\n咁多年恒都做唔到"},{"pid":"5880ebfe84ca91564714c2e65c56cd4031f45b6c","tid":1824145,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"法定假期由12天增至17天，分階段逐步推行<br />\n工聯會表示反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}